                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d963">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/13833.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Agent <persName type="from">Carothers</persName> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Irapttato</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-11-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 19, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>General Gutiérrez conferred with General Villa yesterday afternoon and it was
                    decided that General Villa remain at the head of Convention troops. Progress
                    rapid southward.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Carothers</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
